summary: A joke character my friend created to troll my brother.
descriptionHtml:
This is I'Von Bur'n Stabb, a joke character my cousin created to troll my brother. Don't be fooled by his appearance, he's not an orc. He specializes in fire spells, but he's only level 6.

This is a Vanilla save file, no mods or DLC are needed.

This save has a messed up in-game screenshot because it is actually a converted Xbox 360 savegame and the screenshot was corrupted in the conversion process, but don't worry, the save is completely functional on the PC.

My cousin had given me full permissions to this file.
author: Cousin of Nick3069
